gr.forth.ics.swkm.model2.views
Interface MetaclassView

All Superinterfaces:
Inheritable, RdfNode, View
public interface MetaclassView
extends Inheritable

A object-oriented view of a metaclass.

All methods of this type throw IllegalStateException if the type of this node (i.e. type()) is no longer an metaclass.

Author:
Andreou Dimitris, email: jim.andreou (at) gmail (dot) com

superMetaclasses

Iterable<MetaclassView> superMetaclasses(Transitively transitively)
Returns the (direct or transitive) supermetaclasses of this metaclass. Direct supermetaclasses are requested with Transitively#NO while transitive ones with Transitively#YES.

Parameters:
transitively - whether to return non-direct (i.e. transitive) supermetaclasses too
Returns:
the direct or transitive supermetaclasses of this metaclass
